Olin Corp said its board willelect in April John Johnstone Jr as its chief executiveofficer.    The company said he will succeed John M Henske, who is alsochairman. It said Johnstone, 54, is now president and chiefoperating officer.    Henske, 53, has served as CEO since 1978 and chairman since1980. He will continue as chairman until his retirement in June1988. Reuter&#3;